source: TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_SEQ_00<tab>Sul Uin aches for your attention.
target: TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_SEQ_00<tab>リダ・ラーンのスール＝ウィンは、笑みを浮かべている。

source: TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_TODO_00<tab>Sow everbloom seeds around Lydha Lran.
TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_SULUIN_000_000<tab>Ooh, ooh! Look at me, look at me! I have a task for you!
target: TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_SULUIN_000_000<tab>それじゃあ、ワタシからもお願いをしようかしら？

source: TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_SULUIN_000_001<tab>Lydha Lran is our beloved village, and we want it to always look lovely. And it can't look lovely without flowers blooming. And no flowers bloom lovelier than everblooms!
target:
TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_SULUIN_000_001ここリダ・ラーンは、私たちピクシー族のお気に入りの場所。
だから、いつでも一番かわいくしておかなくちゃならないわ。

source: TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_SULUIN_000_002<tab>So, here are some everbloom seeds. Take them and sow them here, there, and everywhere around the village. Simple as a dimple, yes?
target:
TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_SULUIN_000_002アナタに「」を渡すから、
リダ・ラーンのあちこちに撒いてもらえるかしら？
よろしくね！

source: TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_SULUIN_000_010<tab>No flowers bloom lovelier than everblooms. Take those seeds and sow them here, there, and everywhere around the village!
target:
TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_SULUIN_000_010リダ・ラーンをかわいくするために、
「」を撒いてきてね！

source: TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_PIXIEA03307_000_020<tab>(-Curious Pixie-)Helping us grow flowers, are you? They'll make this house look so much lovelier!
target:
TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_PIXIEA03307_000_020(-興味津々のピクシー族-)あらあらっ？
お花の種を撒いてくれたのね！
素敵、この建物ももっとキレイになるでしょうね！

source: TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_PIXIEA03307_000_021<tab>(-Curious Pixie-)There used to be a city of mortals here. A great big, bustling place called Voeburt or Boevurt or some such. But the sin eaters came and everyone disappeared.
target:
TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_PIXIEA03307_000_021(-興味津々のピクシー族-)ここにはもともと、フッブート王国っていう名前の、
大きなヒトの街があったのよ。
だけど、罪喰いに襲われて、みーんなどこかにいっちゃった！

source: TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_PIXIEA03307_000_022<tab>(-Curious Pixie-)Since then, we pixies have been living here, and we've given the old houses our touch. Lovely, don't you think?
target:
TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_PIXIEA03307_000_022(-興味津々のピクシー族-)だから私たちが住むことにしたの。
こうして、建物をキレイにかざりつけて……ね！

source: TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_PIXIEB03307_000_023<tab>(-Jovial Pixie-)Ooh, I can't wait for the flowers to bloom! Perhaps I'll make pretty curtains out of them!
target:
TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_PIXIEB03307_000_023(-陽気なピクシー族-)わぁい、どんな花が芽吹くかなー。
大きな葉をもつなら、カーテンにもできるよね。
楽しみだなー！

source: TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_SULUIN_000_030<tab>You're done sowing the seeds? Thank you! This shall help Lydha Lran live up to its name─which means “flower house,” in case you weren't aware.
target:
TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_SULUIN_000_030種を撒いてきてくれたのね、ありがとう。
やっぱりたくさんの花が咲いてこそ、
私たちのリダ・ラーン……『花々の館』だわ！

source: TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_SULUIN_000_031<tab>We weren't always here, you know. We used to live deep in a lush forest. It was beautiful beyond compare, but almost all of it was swallowed up by the light.
target:
TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_SULUIN_000_031昔々に住んでいた深い森も、とってもキレイだったのだけど、
ほとんどが「光の氾濫」に呑み込まれてしまったの。

source: TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_SULUIN_000_032<tab>For a while we roamed, but eventually we found a place that men had abandoned. Together with our fellow fae folk, we decided to make it our new home.
target:
TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_SULUIN_000_032それでさまよっていたら、
ヒトが捨ててしまった街があったから、
ほかの妖精と一緒に、住むことにしたというわけ。

source: TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_SULUIN_000_033<tab>The land of everlasting spring─this is our home, and it could be yours too. Forever and ever and ever...
target:
TEXT_LUCKMB106_03307_SULUIN_000_033今では、すっごくお気に入りよ！
アナタもこの、とこしえの春が続く国で、
ずっと、ずーっと、いつまでも幸せに暮らしましょう……？
